Package gov.nyc.doitt.gis.geoclient.test

Class RequiresRestServiceCustomCondtion

java.lang.Object
gov.nyc.doitt.gis.geoclient.test.RequiresRestServiceCustomCondtion
public class RequiresRestServiceCustomCondtion extends Object
Custom method implementation for use as a custom condition with org.junit.jupiter.api.condition.EnabledIf. This class is used instead of a composed annotation because either a matching environment variable or system property will allow the test to run: if both are used to compose an annotation, then both are required. The method is static because it is not part of the test class being annotated.
Since:
2.0
